{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/What-happened-shiphappens/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Dit is het project waar ik aan gewerkt heb gedurende mijn stage bij een maritieme IT startup <a href=\"https://teqplay.nl/\">Teqplay</a>. Het doel van de applicatie was om zoveel mogelijk data van schepen te verzamelen uit verschillende bronnen, te combineren tot één master database en vevolgens in kaart te brengen waar alle data vandaan komt. </p>\n<p>Dus als iemand de vraag heeft over een schip: What happened? ShipHappens heeft het antwoord!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/5a791/shiphappens_1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.21472392638037%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Home Page ShipHappens\"\n        title=\"Home Page ShipHappens\"\n        src=\"/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/a6d36/shiphappens_1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/222b7/shiphappens_1.png 163w,\n/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/ff46a/shiphappens_1.png 325w,\n/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/a6d36/shiphappens_1.png 650w,\n/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/e548f/shiphappens_1.png 975w,\n/static/7b366596cc03099d17a6d4edac2f7376/5a791/shiphappens_1.png 1248w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/6acbf/shiphappens-search.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.50920245398773%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Zoek een ship\"\n        title=\"Zoek een ship\"\n        src=\"/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/a6d36/shiphappens-search.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/222b7/shiphappens-search.png 163w,\n/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/ff46a/shiphappens-search.png 325w,\n/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/a6d36/shiphappens-search.png 650w,\n/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/e548f/shiphappens-search.png 975w,\n/static/92a7a9fb1013ba09580a7b438b1cd51f/6acbf/shiphappens-search.png 1001w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9df3a50e529955b635ab4fabc24afad6/776d3/shiphappens-detailpage.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.852760736196316%; position: