ns_master_table.png 163w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/ff46a/shiphappens_master_table.png 325w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/a6d36/shiphappens_master_table.png 650w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/e548f/shiphappens_master_table.png 975w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/3c492/shiphappens_master_table.png 1300w,\n/static/e78ea67bf382707681b54ed63d04e26d/460fa/shiphappens_master_table.png 1910w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1>Tech</h1>\n<p>Het systeem is geschreven in Kotlin en de front-end is gemaakt met React, er wordt data binnengehaald van de Teqplay API, een CSV file, een XML file en user input. Dit wordt allemaal appart opgeslagen en samengevoegd en vervolgens ook door een eigen API naar buiten beschikbaar gemaakt voor het publiek om te zoeken in de master database.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/4e814/component-overview-shiphappens.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.79754601226993%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"diagram shiphappens\"\n        title=\"diagram shiphappens\"\n        src=\"/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/a6d36/component-overview-shiphappens.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/222b7/component-overview-shiphappens.png 163w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/ff46a/component-overview-shiphappens.png 325w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/a6d36/component-overview-shiphappens.png 650w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/e548f/component-overview-shiphappens.png 975w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/3c492/component-overview-shiphappens.png 1300w,\n/static/4e8c9e958bdfc3a3b56fd01f71cbec3e/4e814/component-overview-shiphappens.png 1335w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"What happened? ShipHappens!","date":"2019-01-25","category":"projects"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/What-happened-shiphappens/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3309693220","3318396998","3649515864","63159454"]}